This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with deep reinforcement learning algorithms and meta-reinforcement learning. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing algorithms that enable agents to learn new skills from small amounts of experience. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics) as it deals with developing efficient algorithms for robots to learn new tasks. The paper also involves computer vision techniques, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, it could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it involves developing algorithms for controlling systems such as robots.
